.account-page__content
  %h2.account-page__content__head
    会員情報入力
  .account-page__content__form
    = form_for(@user, url: user_registration_path) do |f|
      .account-page__content__form__label
        = f.label "ニックネーム", class: ".account-page__content__form__label__name"
        %span.must
          必須
      .account-page__content__form__input
        = f.text_field :nickname, placeholder: '例）朝活くん', class: ".account-page__content__form__input-field"

      .account-page__content__form__label
        = f.label "メールアドレス", class: "account-page__content__form__label__name"
        %span.must
          必須
      .account-page__content__form__input
        = f.email_field :email, autofocus: true, autocomplete: "email", placeholder: 'PC用・携帯用どちらでも可', class: "account-page__content__form__input-field"

      .account-page__content__form__label
        = f.label :password, class: "account-page__content__form__label__name"
        %span.must
          必須
      .account-page__content__form__input
        = f.password_field :password, autocomplete: "new-password", placeholder: "７文字以上の半角英数字", class: "account-page__content__form__input-field"
      
      .account-page__content__form__label
        = f.label :encrypted_password, class: "account-page__content__form__label__name"
        %span.must
          必須
        .account-page__content__form__input
          = f.password_field :encrypted_password, autocomplete: "new-password", placeholder: "７文字以上の半角英数字", class: "account-page__content__form__input-field"
          %p.account-page__content__form__input__message
            ※英字と数字の両方を含めて設定してください

      %h3.identification
        本人確認
      %p.account-page__content__form__message
        安心・安全にご利用いただくために、お客さまの本人情報の登録にご協力ください。他のお客さまに公開されることはありません。
      
      .account-page__content__form__label
        = f.label 'お名前(全角)', class: "account-page__content__form__label__name"
        %span.must
          必須
      .account-page__content__form__input
        .account-page__content__form__input__field
          = f.text_field :first_name, placeholder: '佐藤', class: "account-page__content__form__input__field__name"
          = f.text_field :last_name, placeholder: '太郎', class: "account-page__content__form__input__field__name"
       
      .account-page__content__form__label
        = f.label 'お名前カナ(全角)', class: "account-page__content__form__label__name"
        %span.must
          必須
      .account-page__content__form__input
        .account-page__content__form__input__field
          = f.text_field :first_name_kana, placeholder: 'サトウ', class: "account-page__content__form__input__field__name"
          = f.text_field :last_name_kana, placeholder: 'タロウ', class: "account-page__content__form__input__field__name" 
      
      
      .account-page__content__form__label
        = f.label '生年月日', class: "account-page__content__form__label__name"
        %span.must
          必須
        = f.date_select :birthday, {start_year: 1900, end_year: 2050, prompt: "--"}, {class: "account-page__content__form__input__field__birthday"}

      %p.account-page__content__form__text
        ※本人情報は正しく入力してください。会員登録後、修正するにはお時間を頂く場合があります。
        .account-page__content__form__submit
          = f.submit '次へ進む', class: "account-page__content__form__submit"

    -# = render "devise/shared/links"
